	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#ffffff">
			<div class=content>
			
			<p></p><P><B>Chardok Ring Questの続き</B></P>
<P>（面倒なので訳はしません）<br>
Dorgaに赴き、Gobを虐殺しまわっても特にそれらしきGoblinは出ませんでした。
<br>
海外BBSの情報で、DorgaのCityエリアにGoblinの裏切り者がいるということなので、行ってみたらいました。
<br>
a goblin traitor'という名前のGoblinが（LOC=-22 ,-95）のテントそば（PHあり）。</P>
<P><B>You</B> say, 'Hail, a goblin traitor'
<br>
<B>a goblin traitor</B> says 'Serve the Sarnak do ya? You the one they say they send? I dont know that I believe ya, show a token. Humm show me ya ring if ya got it. <br>


<br>
証である<B>Ring</B>を渡してみます。
<br>a goblin traitor looks relieved when he sees your signet of service and eyes you 
with a bit more respect. ''Good! They tell'd me to wait here for ya, can't say I 
like it but here I sits. Itbe good to be rid of Skargus though, so I be a happy 
one, oh yes. Want to know the [plan] then?'' 
<br>
反応したので聞き込み。
<br>

<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'what plan'
<br>
<B>a goblin traitor</B> says 'Alrighty, listen listen. Skargus used to be a low rankin' nogood.
He made fake story 'bout Gragbar who was the warlord and caused him much
trouble with the chief.
<br>
Gragbar was cast down, chief made Skargus the warlord now. 
<br>
Gragbar is <B>very angry</B>, would take back his position and kill Skargus if he get [evidence] of his treachery. 
<br>

<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'what evidence'
<br>
<B>a goblin traitor</B> makes a terrible face, then spits on the ground before continuing. ''Gragbar
are workin' with the Iksar, bleh Iksar. He sellin' goblin troops as slaves
to Cabilis when he can, sayin' they died in battle at the lake. 
<br>
If we get evidence of that, we get Skargus and kill him. 
<br>
You go to <B>Frontier mountains</B>, find Sarnak there, he knows where we get evidence from. 
<br>
Give him <B>this note</B> from me, and he help ya. Off with ya now, before I get seen with ya.'' 
<br>

<br>FMにSarnakがいるそうですので、外に出てみたら、すぐに「a sarnak spy」がTrackにかかります。
<br>
Dorgaを出て南西に少しの壁のところ。(LOC=1,850 , 3630)
<br>Hailしても反応が無いので、いきなりNoteを渡します。
<br>

<br><B>a sarnak spy</B> reads the note slowly, turning it around in his claws a few times before
completing it. ''I see you spoke with that half-wit goblin! I hate hate
hate it when he sends me a note, his penmanship is almost illegible. 
<br>
I hope he informed you of the situation, he's really not the most dependable
agent of Di'zok, and sadly his note doesn't really make much sense. 
<br>
No matter though, are you ready to [proceed] in this mission?'' 
<br>

<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'I will proceed'
<br>
<B>a sarnak spy</B> says 'Good, here then is what you must do. 
<br>
It's pretty simple actually and even one such as you should have no troubles.

<br>
Skargus has been trading in slaves with the Iksar. He has a courier there
visits the outskirts of Cabilis and sends weekly reports back to Droga.

<br>
If we could get <B>that report</B>, Skargus would be finished. Will you go to Cabilis and [get the report]? 
<br>

<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'I will get the report'
<br>
<B>a sarnak spy</B> scowls at you, clearly unimpressed by your efforts.''Of course you'll
go get the report fool, but do you think that the courier will just give
it to you?'' <B>
<br>
The sarnak</B> shakes his head sadly. ''Okay, look. Go into Droga and try to get a <B>warlord's insignia</B> off one of the goblins in there. 
<br>
Take this forged note to the courier I've written out, along with the insignia to <B>Warslik's woods</B> and give it to the courier. 
<br>
With luck, he'll believe you work for Skargus and <B>give you the report</B>. 
<br>
If you get the report, <B>find Gragbar </B>in Droga and give it to him .'' 
<br>

<br>
Goblinの奴隷商人のSkargusのエージェントであると騙すためDorga内で<B>warlord's insignia</B>を拾います。
<br>
GoblinからのRandomDropで、20匹も殺せば出てくるでしょう。見た目は盾でNoDropです。
<br>
これとSarnakから貰ったNoteを渡しにWarsilks Woodへ。
<br>

<br>
Cabilisに向かって左側の建物（Ikserが居ない方）の2階に、a shady goblin
というGoblinがいます。（かなりの長時間Repopらしい）
<br>
FacはIndiff。
<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'Hail, a shady goblin'
<br>
<B>a shady goblin</B> says 'If yer not my contact ya best be movin' on. Got no time to waste on ya. 
<br>
このあと進まないので、証である<B>warlord's insignia</B>とNoteを渡します。
<br>

<br>
<B>a shady goblin</B> gapes at the note in puzzlement, obviously a bit concerned by it. The
courier looks at the note for more than a minute, then looks at you, and
back at the note. ''Errm.. welp, dunno what to make of the note. If I know
the right of it, Skargus finally got him some girly to do his writin' for
him. 
<br>
Ooooh I bet she a tasty one, graarr. If I was warlord I know I'd have me
a girly too. Gah, take this report and get outta my sight. 
<br>

<br>
何が書いてあったのでしょうかw
<br>
Goblinは消え、Reportを貰います。あとはこのReportをDorgaにいるであろう<B>Gragbar</B>に渡せばよいようです。
<br>
<B>Gragbar</B>は大変怒ってるらしく、The angry goblinという名前で長時間POPする模様（LOC=120,1900あたりをRoamingしてるGobがPHとの噂）。
<br>
捜査チームは一路、Dorgaに向かうが、Raidが始まったのでそっち行きましたw
<br>

<br>
噂によれば、2段階目のRingは
<br>
AC+5 STR+5 STA+5 CHA+2 INT+2 WIS+2 HP+85 MANA+50だとか。Wow
<br>
（つづく）</P><p></p>
