		<td bgcolor="#ffffff">
			<div class=content>
			
			<p></p><P>Chardokに入ってすぐのところに小さなSarnak、<B>Herald Telcha</B>がいます。
<br>
Dorgaで遊んでいたら知らぬ間にFacが<B>Warmly</B>だったので話してみました。</P>
<P><B>You</B> say, 'Hail, Herald Telcha'
<br>
<B>Herald Telcha</B> says 'Hail to you, lesser being! It is good to see you seeking the enlightenment
and satisfaction that can only come from serving the Sarnak! 

Experience for yourself the joy of fealty to our Lord the Overking Bathezid
Dizok! 
<br>
I am Telcha, lesser apprentice sub-herald in training to the Court of Dizok
and I stand ready to welcome those who would serve our noble Overking.
Are you here to [aid] us ? 
<br>

<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'I will aid you'
<br>
<B>Herald Telcha</B> says 'Ah, so good of you to strive to improve yourself! 
<br>
So often members of your pathetic lesser races plod along in ignorance,
unaware of the most Noble empire of the Dizok. Enough though of the chit-chat,
as Im sure you are most eager to make yourself useful! 
<br>
Before you may enter our worthy city and be looked upon as a valuable servant,
you must prove your worth to our [cause]. 
<br>

<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'What cause?'
<br>
<B>Herald Telcha</B> says 'The first task I shall set you is the slaying of <B>goblins!</B> 
<br>
Ooh, how very heroic you must feel to finally have a worthy goal guiding
your previously menial existance! 
<br>
Yes, go forth from here and journey to <B>Droga</B>, stronghold of our enemies. 
<br>
Slay the warriors and menials of the Mountain Death Clan, bring havoc to
their homes. 
<br>
Return to me with <B>proof of your deeds</B>, to raise in your standing with the Dizok. 
<br>
Bring me [tokens] of many dead goblins, and one day you shall walk among
us. 
<br>

<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'what is tokens?'
<br>
<B>Herald Telcha</B> says 'As proof of your deeds I shall require either <B>2 Mountain Death mineral salts</B>, or a patch of <B>green goblin skin</B>. 

<br>Bring me many of these, as you bring destruction on the goblin city, and
I shall speak to my superiours of your efforts on our behalf. 

<br>Do enough for our cause, and I shall reward you directly. 

<br>Return to me later and remind me that you serve the Sarnak, and I may have a <B>ring</B> for you if you are worthy. 

<br>
<br>
<B>Temple of Dorga</B>に向かい、Goblinsから出る「<B>Mountain Death Mineral salt</B>」と「<B>Green Goblin skin</B>」を集めます。

<br>そして2個のSaltとGoblinSkinを渡すだけ。


<br><br>
<B>Mountain Death Mineral salt</B>の場合
<br>
<B>Herald Telcha</B> says 'Ah, most excellent!  You are sure to be more highly valued as our servant once I speak to my masters of this!  Mountain Death Mineral Salts, they shall grace the Overkings table this very night!  Be off, minion!  Fetch us some more salts to prove your value!'
<br>
Your faction standing with SarnakCollective got better.
<br>
Your faction standing with BroodOfDizok got better
<br>
Your faction standing with GoblinsOfMountainDeath got worse


<br><br>
<B>Green Goblin skin</B>の場合
<br>
<B>Herald Telcha</B> says 'Green Goblin Skin! You have indeed been busy! I shall speak to my
masters of this, continue your good work and return to me with more skins.
'
<br>
Your faction standing with SarnakCollective got better.
<br>
Your faction standing with BroodOfDizok got better
<br>
Your faction standing with GoblinsOfMountainDeath got worse
<br>

<br>
いずれもFac変動のみ。ていうかSarnakCollective上がるねw
<br>
RewardないのはFacが足りないのかも？<br>
そこで次のKeywordを言ってみると・・・<br>
<br>
<B>You</B> say, 'I serve the sarnak'<br>
<B>Herald Telcha</B> says 'You Indeed you do my friend, indeed you do! Walk among us in safety, wear this ring as a symbol of your service to our cause. Continue your efforts in our war on the goblins, and your rewards shall increase. Return to me your ring, along with the <B>head of the Drogan Warlord Skargus</B>, and Ill give you an even greater badge of honor. Good day to you, servant of the Sarnak. <br>
<br>
Ring（MAGIC LORE NO DROP AC+2 CHA:+1 INT:+1 WIS:+1 HP:+65 MANA:+45）を貰いました！<br>
<IMG src="ring.jpg" border="0"><br>
Ringを貰うにはFacはWarmly以上が必要です。<br>Facが足りない場合は以下のMessageが。<br><br>
<B>Herald Telcha</B> says 'You have not yet done enough service for the Sarnak Collective,
and my Dizok Masters. <br>
Return to me when you have done more, and I may reward you with a ring
of service.<br>
<br>
head of the Drogan Warlord SkargusをGetできれば、もっと良いものに交換してくれるようですが、そんなGobはどこにも見つけられません・・・（つづく）</BODY><p></p>
